snippet.title: Techno Ruhez
snippet.description:
Hi Guys! My name is Ruhez Amrelia, and I'm a 28 year old Youtuber. On this channel I bring you guys reviews on all the latest and greatest phones, Mobile & PC, Daily Tech News With Tips & Tutorials.

My goal is to intrigue you with the latest reviews about new smartphones,Laptops,Tv's and Gadgets, Inform complete beginners on how to use their devices and show competent users little tricks that will make you say, "Oh that's cool, I didn't know it could do that." And, I hope to entertain you with passion and a little bit of humour along the way. 

Subscribe for free technology advice, daily tech video updates and crazy giveaways! :P

Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/AmreliaRuhez
Follow me on Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/technoruhez/
Follow and Like my Page on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/technoruhez

Please Dont Forget to Like, Share & Subscribe

https://www.youtube.com/c/Technoruhez

For Business Enquiries: technoreviewww@gmail.com
